{"tid":58030,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[冬天食雪糕,夏天打邊爐]你地食大筒雪糕個陣會點食?","createTime":"2016-12-28T13:27:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T14:14:45.000Z","uid":63626,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bb6cf245dbcdaa9aef4a568ffa9333c619b830e6","tid":58030,"uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:27:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.nestle.com.hk/brands/icecream/Dreyers/PublishingImages/Dreyers-06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nestle.com.hk%2Fbrands%2Ficecream%2FDreyers%2FPublishingImages%2FDreyers-06.jpg&h=fa0809e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即係呢款dryers咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正皮:拎個匙羹就咁&quot;畢&quot;食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負皮:拎多個碗&quot;畢&quot;落去再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我就係用正皮個個方法食,事關得我一個自己食上圖個隻雪糕<br />\n不過我就一定食唔哂,食夠就放入雪櫃<br />\n但我老豆老母就屌我冇家教同唔衛生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問佢地點解又答唔撚到,一味係度鬧我<br />\n都唔知係咪成日上facebook share個D垃圾台灣網睇到壞腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食乜都會又病又生cancer又死人 <br />\n真係on撚鳩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 衛生先唔講(未讀過bio),點解一筒過咁拎住黎食會冇家教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a419a60af9c33aae01f8706295830baa9ee41cf3","tid":58030,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:29:02.000Z","msg":"唔想洗碗"},{"pid":"e92acf147c3358e82841c18b0cc13795b4084659","tid":58030,"uid":28834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:30:23.000Z","msg":"我以為你問大甜筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我會就咁用匙成盒食 咁樣先夠滋味<br />\n食夠成盒雪番雪櫃下次繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73cb59ac67c5ce6987628dfa8cecc28c501fc51f","tid":58030,"uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:31:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我以為你問大甜筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我會就咁用匙成盒食 咁樣先夠滋味<br />\n食夠成盒雪番雪櫃下次繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就係因為咁先比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2fe6cc4fb78275d06acc8334d3d35adb7e9906","tid":58030,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:35:47.000Z","msg":"直接成盒食既話 你一路食佢一路溶 佢溶完你又雪返硬佢下次食 食撚死你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408812f5afaa72c6981b577450635b287281eccc","tid":58030,"uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T14:14:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直接成盒食既話 你一路食佢一路溶 佢溶完你又雪返硬佢下次食 食撚死你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩問題<br />\nbtw,冬天食冇溶得咁勁<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUPTdTTS8kpJqzr3bFScxAPz6oj5K9ckJfDSndEVJhLQ9?filename=2Pv1H.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Pv1H.gif&h=d1c87edc&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}